BC Partners Buys 78.7% of Retailer Coin, to Make Bid on Rest of Company

-- B y   J e r r o l d   C o l t e n   a n d   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i
-- 
2011-05-09T05:56:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-09/bc-partners-buys-78-7-of-retailer-coin-to-make-bid-on-rest-of-company.html
BC Partners  said in a statement today
that it will buy 78.7 percent of  Gruppo Coin SpA (GCN)  and launch an
offer on the rest of the company at 6.50 euros per share.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jerrold Colten at 
 jcolten@bloomberg.net  